title: IQ and Aptitude Tests: Assess Your Verbal, Numerical
description:
IQ and Aptitude Tests: Assess Your Verbal, Numerical and Spatial Reasoning Skills by Philip Carter

ISBN: 0749461950 | 2011 | EPUB | 192 pages | 5 MB


IQ and Aptitude Tests contains 400 practice questions along with answers, explanations, and a guide to assessing performance. The questions are organized into four IQ tests together with verbal, spatial, and numerical aptitude tests. These include tests of word meanings, grammar and comprehension, advanced verbal aptitude, logical analysis, mental arithmetic, numerical sequences, and number problems
